      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It's in absolutely stunning shape and has been pampered since day one. There isn't a single blemish to be found\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken so much pride in keeping it perfect, and I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
