    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a recently overhauled dual-VANOS system. The rod bearings have been proactively replaced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. It retains its original Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing precise engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been refreshed with OEM-spec bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the sharp, analog handling characteristics these chassis are known for. No fluid leaks, no codes, and an immaculate undercarriage make this a definitive enthusiast-spec M3.",
      "price": 48500.0,
