      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the original factory floor mats have been protected by weather-guards since purchase. Every electronic component, button, and switch functions with factory-set tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history from the original dealership. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or inclement weather use. Included are all original keys, the original window sticker, and a comprehensive binder containing every service receipt. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule quality machine.",
